rows.label: qst001502_msg001
rows.name: おや　何か御用でしょうか？

rows.label: qst001502_msg002
rows.name:
こ　これは[ML:Dash ]！
きみ！　これを一体どこで！？

rows.label: qst001502_msg003
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]なるほど
わざわざ届けてくださったのですね

rows.label: qst001502_msg004
rows.name:
この情報が他国に知られたら
どうなっていたことか[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst001502_msg005
rows.name:
本当に助かりました
ありがとうございます

rows.label: qst001502_msg006
rows.name:
こちら　報酬の品になります
どうぞお受け取りください

rows.label: qst001502_msg007
rows.name:
これはメレフ特別執権官殿
如何しましたか？

rows.label: qst001502_msg008
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]なんと
メレフ殿自ら届けてくださったのですか！

rows.label: qst001502_msg009
rows.name:
この情報がインヴィディアなどに
渡っていたら今頃大変なことになって[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst001502_msg010
rows.name:
ああ　このような場所ですべき話では
ありませんでしたね
申しわけありません

rows.label: qst001502_msg011
rows.name:
ともかく　本当に助かりました
ありがとうございます！

rows.label: qst001502_msg0001
rows.name: Hello, citizen. Something the matter?

rows.label: qst001502_msg0002
rows.name:
T-this!
Where did you-?!

rows.label: qst001502_msg0003
rows.name:
...Ooohh, I see.
You went to all that trouble.

rows.label: qst001502_msg0004
rows.name:
I shudder to think what might happen
if this information got into the other
countries' hands...

rows.label: qst001502_msg0005
rows.name:
If Emperor Nefer and Special Inquisitor
Meleph's past schedules became public
knowledge, they'd be in deep water!

rows.label: qst001502_msg0006
rows.name:
Oop, pardon, I overstepped.
You heard nothing.

rows.label: qst001502_msg0007
rows.name:
You've been a great help, really
you have. Thank you very much.

rows.label: qst001502_msg0008
rows.name: This is your reward. Take it, please.

rows.label: qst001502_msg00101
rows.name:
Special Inquisitor Meleph!
Is something the matter?

rows.label: qst001502_msg00102
rows.name:
There was a case, wasn't there, of a
spy hiding top-secret intelligence inside
a Noog Skeeter?!

rows.label: qst001502_msg00103
rows.name: I have retrieved it.

rows.label: qst001502_msg00104
rows.name:
...Wow!
Meleph-sama Flamebringer herself
did us the honor of recovering it?!

rows.label: qst001502_msg00105
rows.name:
And to think that Emperor Nefer and
Meleph-sama's childhood diaries could
have been halfway to Invidia by now...

rows.label: qst001502_msg00107
rows.name:
I beg your pardon!
A slip of the tongue, is all!

rows.label: qst001502_msg00108
rows.name:
Regardless, this is a great help.
Thank you very much!

rows.label: qst001502_msg00109
rows.name:
Don't mention it.
All in a day's work.
